				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/299/sibling-rivalry">Sibling Rivalry</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
							By <a class="meta-article-contributors" href="/contributors/our-readers">Our Readers</a></li><li><a href="/issues/299">November 2000</a></li></ul>

		

					</div>


